# ── Rust ──
target/
# Cargo.lock 必须提交：NovaCode 是产出二进制的应用，锁定依赖版本保证 CI 与本地构建可复现，
# 避免 CI 全新解析拿到不兼容的传递依赖（如 time crate 触发 coherence 编译错误）。

# ── Node ──
node_modules/
dist/
.turbo/

# ── Tauri ──
apps/desktop/src-tauri/target/
apps/desktop/dist/

# ── OS ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── IDE ──
.vscode/settings.json
.idea/
*.suo
*.user

# ── Env ──
.env
.env.*

# ── Dev collaboration rules (local only, never upload) ──
.dev-rules.md

# ── Internal migration scaffolding (local only, keeps legacy names out of the public repo) ──
NOVA_CODE_MIGRATION_PLAN.md

# ── Claude Code local settings ──
.claude/
